 <H1>How Do You Design UI�s Now?</H1> 
 <P><UL></P>

<P><LI><H2>Good: 

</H2></P>

<P><UL></P>

<P><LI>Gain real insight into the user�s tasks and background

<LI>Build and review UI models and prototypes

</UL></UL><UL></P>

<P><LI><H2>OK:

</H2></P>

<P><UL></P>

<P><LI>Implement prototype with a GUI builder, focus on layout

<LI>Imitate successful or familiar UI�s and follow guidelines

